CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,FA man from Derby has been jailed after
OL,8,Fhe crashed into a car carrying a
OL,9,Fpregnant woman whilst online gambling
OL,10,Fon the A50.
OL,12,FAfter Jack Bentley crashed into the
OL,13,Fback of the Nissan X Trail, the mother
OL,14,Fwas rushed to the hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,FThe woman, who was a passenger, had to
OL,8,Fhave an emergency C-section and
OL,9,Fsuffered serious injuries. Her baby
OL,10,Fwas born pre-mature, and both of its
OL,11,Flungs later collapsed. Her child had
OL,12,Fto spend the first weeks of their life
OL,13,Fin intensive care.
OL,15,FTwo other children in the car also
OL,16,Fsuffered injuries, the driver suffered
OL,17,Fwhiplash, and the family's pet dog was
OL,18,Fseriously injured and needed emergency
OL,19,Fsurgery.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,FBentley pleaded guilty at Derby Crown
OL,8,FCourt. On 11th February, he was jailed
OL,9,Ffor two years and four months. He has
OL,10,Falso been disqualified from driving
OL,11,Ffor three years and two months.
OL,13,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,14,Fwoman said: "I needed an emergency
OL,15,Fcaesarean due to my baby being in
OL,16,Fdistress. I found this very traumatic
OL,17,Fand didn't want my baby to be born
OL,18,Flike that and that early.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,F"My baby was born without skin-to-skin
OL,8,Fcontact, and my partner and I had to
OL,9,Fwait to see her. When you have a baby,
OL,10,Fyou expect to be in a bubble with your
OL,11,Fpartner and newborn baby, but we were
OL,12,Fseparated across three wards in the
OL,13,Fhospital and missed out on so much in
OL,14,Fthose early moments.
OL,16,F"No mother or father should have to go
OL,17,Fthrough this.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,F"The next three weeks we spent in
OL,8,Fhospital getting our baby strong
OL,9,Fenough to come home. I was having to
OL,10,Fvisit my baby on a hospital bed to
OL,11,Fwatch her in her incubator.
OL,13,F"I remember being there watching when
OL,14,Fall the nurses and doctors rushed
OL,15,Faround because her lung had collapsed
OL,16,Fand I had to lay there scared for her.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,F"Hours later the other lung also
OL,8,Fcollapsed. She wasn't strong enough
OL,9,Ffor the world yet. For my first
OL,10,Fpregnancy, this was a very traumatic
OL,11,Fexperience and one no parent expects
OL,12,For wants to experience."
OL,14,FPC Richard Morris from Derbyshire
OL,15,FPolice said: "This was an appalling
OL,16,Fdisplay of driving by Bentley, who
OL,17,Fspent the majority of his journey
OL,18,Fdistracted by being on his phone.
OL,26,@tD@XO]wD@NOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,F"From watching the dashcam footage, it
OL,8,Fwas clear that had he been paying
OL,9,Fattention, he would have seen the
OL,10,Fqueue of traffic in front of him and
OL,11,Fbeen able to stop in time.
OL,13,F"Instead, he was more focused on his
OL,14,Fphone and subsequently ploughed into
OL,15,Fthe Nissan, causing extensive injuries
OL,16,Fto the occupants and their family dog.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,F"The fact that his actions caused a
OL,8,Fwoman to give birth prematurely and
OL,9,Fleft a tiny baby spending the first
OL,10,Ffew weeks of their life in intensive
OL,11,Fcare is nothing short of despicable.
OL,13,F"I know that the physical, mental and
OL,14,Femotional trauma from this incident
OL,15,Fcontinues to impact on this family,
OL,16,Fwho were simply going out their day
OL,17,Fwhen this wholly avoidable collision
OL,18,Foccurred.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772100320
OL,3,CDriver jailed after crashing into
OL,4,Cpregnant mother whilst online gambling
OL,5,Con A50
OL,7,F"My thoughts remain with them as they
OL,8,Fcontinue their recovery and I hope
OL,9,Fthat knowing that Bentley is behind
OL,10,Fbars provides them with some form of
OL,11,Fcomfort as they look ahead to the
OL,12,Ffuture."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/9
